---

<section id="services" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
        Our Services
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-gray-500">
        Comprehensive HVAC solutions for all your needs
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Installation</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Professional installation of new HVAC systems with expert guidance on the best solutions for your space.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Repair</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Quick and reliable repair services for all makes and models of HVAC equipment.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Maintenance</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Regular maintenance programs to keep your system running efficiently and prevent costly breakdowns.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>